des:
Do you miss FRIENDS? Do you miss the jokes? Do you want to hear the funniest dialogues between the Friends cast? Central Perk is here to make you re-live those amazing moments! Made by FRIENDS fans for FRIENDS fans.

Enable this skill to hear the funniest dialogues between the six characters including Ross, Rachel, Chandler, Joey, Monica and Phoebe. These curated funny dialogues from the show are sure to brighten your day and take you on a trip down the memory lane.

Made by Vyral with Love!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
